13 of the North Carolina Investment Authority are exempt from this Chapter and shall be accounted
14 for as provided in Article 6 of Chapter 147 of the General Statutes."
15 SECTION 4.3.(b) This section is effective July 1, 2025.
16
17 PART V. EFFECTIVE DATE
18 SECTION 5.1. Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective when it becomes
19 law.
